If you’re still reading this board, and you haven't given your stuff away and quit.<br>
<br>
Don't.<br>
<br>
You are a good monk, and you’re just a kid.<br>
Don't post here though if you’re looking for people to advise you when you have done something wrong.<br>
<br>
This is the blast furnace.  Had you posted in the General forum, you probably would have gotten flamed anyway and the thread would likely have been moved here so the piranhas could swarm on.<br>
<br>
I have grouped with you, you have been in guilds with my alts, and you still have friends.  <br>
<br>
I do not in any way condone what you did.  But I am not going to flame you for it.  I am going to tell you to do everything in your power to make it right, and tell you have burned quite a few bridges.  <br>
<br>
Choose your actions very carefully in the future and be prepared.  You are going to get more shots taken at you.<br>
<br>
Chimeraa<br>
